summary: Jude Law talks about difference between the Fantastic Beasts set vs. Captain Marvel set when it came to preventing spoiler...
caption:
Jude Law talks about difference between the Fantastic Beasts set vs. Captain Marvel set when it came to preventing spoiler leakage: 

– There was a guy hired, I promise you, on [the Captain Marvel] set that…they’d say, “Mr. Law, they’re ready for you,” and you step out in your suit, and he’d go, “Put the cloak on, put the cloak on!! Hide!! Put the hood up!” I mean, everywhere you went. My children visited the set, and they were running in, “Sign the NDAs!! Who are these guys..?!” It was tight.

title: First Look at Skrull Leader LEGO Figure from Captain Marvel
body:
First Look at Skrull Leader LEGO Figure from Captain Marvel

The LEGO figurine for Captain Marvel’s Skrull leader Talos has been revealed. Though mostly indistinguishable from any other Skrull character from the movie, it highlights recognizable features that are as movie-accurate as they are comic-accurate.

Predating the events of Iron Man, Captain Marvel centers around former U.S. Air Force fighter pilot Carol Danvers (Brie Larson) as her pursuit to…

Let’s grow those shoulders!! Go heavy, breath in through your nose and out through your mouth.

Rest 30 seconds between exercises and 90 seconds between sets.

Superset #1

Military barbell press — 3 sets x 10 reps

Lateral raises — 3 sets x 10 reps

Superset #2

Dumbbell shoulder press — 3 sets x 10 reps

Front raises — 3 sets x 10 reps

Superset #3
